climbs.name: The Rubber Room
climbs.fa: Keith Bruckner and Raleigh Collins, November 1992

content.description: Starts behind a pine tree and climbs a vertical crack that ends just below the top and then a short bit of face leads to the top.
content.location:
Located on the narrow south end of the rock facing the north side of

Scary Rock

.

climbs.name: Keith's Cruise
climbs.fa: Keith Bruckner and Raleigh Collins, November 1992

content.description:
Climb a slightly left-slanting crack/seam which jogs left and then joins

Grain Block

where the crack starts arcing right and then continue as per that route past a bolt to the top.
content.protection: Gear to 2 inches, bolt, 2 bolt rap (all 3/8")
content.location:
The vertical crack/seam just right of

Grain Block

.

climbs.name: Grain Block
climbs.fa: Keith Bruckner and Raleigh Collins, November 1992

content.description: Climbs the right-slanting crack as it curves up and right and then exits up on face past a solitary bolt where the crack starts to go horizontal.
content.protection: Gear to 2.5 inches, 1 bolt, 2 bolt rap (all 3/8")
content.location:
The obvious right-slanting crack just right of

Bruckner's Boogie

.

climbs.name: Freudian Slip
climbs.fa: Raleigh Collins and Keith Bruckner, November 1992

content.description: Climbs a left-slanting crack past several horizontals to a stance with a block and then up runout face to the top.
content.location:
Crack to face between

Keith's Cruise

and

The Rubber Room

.

climbs.name: Bruckner's Boogie
climbs.fa: Keith Bruckner and Raleigh Collins, November 1992

content.description: Climb a slab along a seam that steepens at the top. There are anchors atop this route that the other routes on the wall share.
content.location:
Center of the west face and across from

Shock Therapy

on

Split Personality Rock

.
